column17: All prizes are converted to euro's based on exchange rates of that time
Viewership: Final match being watched worldwide
Cincinnati Open: Prize pool is the same, but male winners earn more then female winners
Qatar Masters: No female tournament in 2010, 2011 onwards bigger prize pool for men
Rome Masters has bigger Prize pool than female

Some WTA 500 tournaments are combined with an ATP 250 event, likely to increase overall attendance and financial support. This approach may help ensure sufficient funding for both events' prize pools.
